Logic 20 prevents:

‚ùå Informal side negotiations
‚ùå Hidden financial concessions
‚ùå Escalation to litigation due to poor documentation
‚ùå Operational paralysis
‚ùå Biased internal decisions
‚ùå Repeated supplier misconduct

