# 1Ô∏è‚É£8Ô∏è‚É£ STRATEGIC IMPACT

Logic 20:

* Protects institutional stability
* Reduces legal exposure
* Encourages professional supplier relationships
* Builds trust through predictable enforcement
* Converts conflict into controlled governance

It transforms disputes from chaotic breakdowns into **structured governance events**.

